    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable condition. Meticulously preserved and showing no signs of wear, it retains its original showroom luster both inside and out. Every component has been subjected to rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our highest standards of mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or driver to acquire a vehicle that has been maintained with an absolute disregard for expense.",
